add .dockerignore

Instructions to map data file to relevant place:
- .:/data


Add docker env params (e.g. location of data write out), read this:
https://nickjanetakis.com/blog/dockerize-a-flask-celery-and-redis-application-with-docker-compose




# Create dump
docker exec -t crisis-data_db_1 pg_dump -c -U username eventdb | gzip > dump_$(date +"%Y-%m-%d").gz

# Restore db from dump
gzip -d -c dump.gz | cat | docker exec -i crisis-data_db_1 psql -U username eventdb



